metadata.name: Unravel People's COOLCATS
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's COOLCATS, which represents an inactive state of pCOOLCATS. Users can participate in a new Cool Cats acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's COOLCATS as credit. upCOOLCATS can be claimed into pCOOLCATS when the subscription successfully acquires a new Cool Cats
